node.text: Today the coolest soccer pub in town @toffeeclubpdx closed it’s doors. Like many of us they looked at their dream and realized it wasn’t sustainable during #covid19. If you’re out there thinking that your favorite restaurants will survive because they’re so good there’s no way you can imagine them closing, think twice. We’re all fighting hard but unless people come in or order take out we will not be around for too much longer. So if you’re in a position of being able to go out and spend money at a small local restaurant do so, we need you. If you sell products to restaurants and they support your business pay it forward, show up because if we don’t make it nor will you. #inittogether #wecandohardthings #pandemic2020 #toosmalltofail #saverestaurants #eatlocal #localrestaurants #eaterpdx #portlandrestaurants #hospitality
